# Brand assets (locked)

Logo and favicon are **mandatory** and must not be removed, replaced with text, or pointed to external URLs.

## Single source of truth

- `src/config/brand.ts` — all paths and metadata icon definitions
- `src/components/brand/SiteLogo.tsx` — header logo (uses `BRAND_ASSETS` only)
- `public/img/brand/` — logo + favicon PNG files (deployed with hosting)
- `src/app/icon.png` and `src/app/apple-icon.png` — Next.js metadata icons (keep in sync with `brand.ts`)

## Rules

- Never revert header to text-only `SectorCalc` branding.
- Never delete or gitignore `public/img/brand/*` or app icon files.
- Do not swap favicon/logo unless the user provides new approved assets and asks explicitly.
- Metadata (`createPageMetadata`, root layout) must include `BRAND_METADATA_ICONS`.
